    "Scamming, in general, is a deplorable act that is ethically, morally, and legally condemned in society.",
    "It not only negatively impacts individuals financially, but also can cause immense emotional distress.",
    "In addition, it's illegal and punishable under the law which could lead to imprisonment.",
    "This profession does not contribute positively to the economy, community or society at large.",
    "This act undermines trust in online transactions and communication, hindering the growth of a digital society."
